You...

125
00:07:08,595 --> 00:07:10,163
You have money, big sister?

126
00:07:10,163 --> 00:07:11,431
Oh, of course not.

127
00:07:11,431 --> 00:07:13,533
My budget is still
incredibly strapped.

128
00:07:13,533 --> 00:07:15,268
So we need to figure out
how we can get

129
00:07:15,268 --> 00:07:16,936
to the beach
on the cheap, you know?

130
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:35,655
You sounded like you had
some sort of great idea,

131
00:07:35,655 --> 00:07:37,357
but you're just suggesting
we hitch hike?

132
00:07:37,357 --> 00:07:38,692
I know what to do!

133
00:07:38,692 --> 00:07:41,528
You can stop a car with
a sexy wink, am I right?

134
00:07:41,528 --> 00:07:42,595
All right!

135
00:07:42,962 --> 00:07:44,631
My thighs will shoot them down.

136
00:07:44,631 --> 00:07:46,733
Oh, please stop that, Hasegawa.

137
00:07:46,733 --> 00:07:49,469
Our chances are going to go
from low to none at all.

138
00:07:51,805 --> 00:07:53,506
I suppose I have no choice.

139
00:07:55,675 --> 00:07:56,576
First, what you need to do

140
00:07:56,576 --> 00:07:59,012
is put both of your hands
on top of your head.

141
00:08:01,014 --> 00:08:02,949
And next, suck in your stomach...

142
00:08:04,951 --> 00:08:07,854
then stoop forward to show off
your ample cleavage.

143
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:15,562
