144
00:08:26,473 --> 00:08:28,007
And here we go.

145
00:08:28,875 --> 00:08:31,244
Can you turn up
the air conditioner, please?

146
00:08:35,148 --> 00:08:36,783
Thank you so much for this.

147
00:08:36,783 --> 00:08:38,151
God, are we so lucky

148
00:08:38,151 --> 00:08:40,754
that we just happened
to be going the same way?

149
00:08:41,454 --> 00:08:44,090
Hey, driver, can you play
my mix tape?

150
00:08:44,090 --> 00:08:46,192
Kagura, Kagura, Kagura,
you're hurting me!

151
00:08:46,192 --> 00:08:48,628
Don't move! Your knee is pushing
into my wounds.

152
00:08:48,628 --> 00:08:49,596
We should be treated better

153
00:08:49,596 --> 00:08:51,598
since we put our lives
on the line to stop the car.

154
00:08:51,598 --> 00:08:52,632
It's so hot in here!

155
00:08:52,632 --> 00:08:53,767
Hot and stinky!

156
00:08:53,767 --> 00:08:55,535
You're using way too much
stuff in your hair!

157
00:08:55,902 --> 00:08:58,500
Play "My Best Music"
mix tape now!

158
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:01,674
