to say how hot it is?

188
00:10:42,075 --> 00:10:44,177
It only makes you
feel even hotter.

189
00:10:44,944 --> 00:10:46,179
That's right.

190
00:10:46,179 --> 00:10:49,449
If he can speak out like that,
then he's doing just fine.

191
00:10:50,149 --> 00:10:53,486
But when you start slurring
your words and you fall down...

192
00:10:56,956 --> 00:10:58,391
You're awesome, Hasegawa.

193
00:10:58,391 --> 00:11:01,361
