202
00:11:22,448 --> 00:11:23,917
Oh, there's the beach!

203
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:41,634
Guys, let's go!

204
00:11:41,634 --> 00:11:43,002
‐Yeah.
‐Yeah.

205
00:12:12,999 --> 00:12:16,035
Oh, an alien, huh?

206
00:12:16,035 --> 00:12:17,737
