207
00:12:17,737 --> 00:12:18,972
Really?

208
00:12:19,906 --> 00:12:21,908
Well, this will be a big help!

209
00:12:21,908 --> 00:12:24,344
Summer is supposed to be
the busiest season, you know,

210
00:12:24,344 --> 00:12:26,980
