because of the alien!

211
00:12:26,980 --> 00:12:28,648
We're really in trouble.

212
00:12:29,315 --> 00:12:31,317
So then, was it you who...

213
00:12:31,317 --> 00:12:33,653
Posted the bounty
on the alien in the water...?

214
00:12:33,987 --> 00:12:35,054
Right...

215
00:12:35,054 --> 00:12:36,856
Yeah, that was me,
that was me.

216
00:12:36,856 --> 00:12:40,793
Yeah, but I didn't expect anyone
to come here to collect.

217
00:12:41,127 --> 00:12:42,295
The truth is...

218
00:12:42,295 --> 00:12:45,131
I was actually kind of joking
about it over drinks one night.

219
00:12:45,131 --> 00:12:48,601
So I never thought somebody
would actually come here.

220
00:12:51,838 --> 00:12:54,273
Joking about it
over drinks one night?

221
00:12:54,273 --> 00:12:56,209
Hey man, we're actually
serious about this

222
00:12:56,209 --> 00:12:58,311
because our livelihoods
are on the line.

223
00:12:58,945 --> 00:13:01,547
A man's gotta put his life on
the line even when he's joking

224
00:13:01,547 --> 00:13:03,516
and we're gonna make sure
you keep your end of the deal.

225
00:13:03,516 --> 00:13:04,517
Hey, wait!

226
00:13:04,517 --> 00:13:06,219
Calm down, calm down!

227
00:13:06,219 --> 00:13:08,554
No, don't worry! I'll pay you.
I have money.

228
00:13:08,554 --> 00:13:10,857
I have it all prepared, I swear.

229
00:13:13,926 --> 00:13:15,294
You are a liar!

230
00:13:15,294 --> 00:13:18,064
Your fried noodles
are overcooked.

231
00:13:18,064 --> 00:13:20,400
